Package: pubmedRecords
Type: Package
Title: Get and format NCBI PubMed records for text mining
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2016-08-07
Author: Peter Kamerman <peter.kamerman@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Peter Kamerman <peter.kamerman@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/kamermanpr/pubmedRecords
BugReports: https://github.com/kamermanpr/pubmedRecords/issues
Description: This package provides tools to download records from the NCBI PubMed database based on user input, and to format the data in a form that can be used by the text mining package ’tm’. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Depends: 
	R (>= 3.3.1),
